@OBF<br>
1-You're voting Peabody, so what do you think of his latest posts? <br>
2-What does your most recent post mean?

@Coron - I did.  You are effort posting a bit more recently.  Try more subtle shit posting, I'm working on developing it myself after my last game's horrific debacle.  I see the brilliance in it now.  Exhibit A:<br>
<br>
@Herr - <blockquote class="uncited"><div>What did you gain from putting Greg at L-1?</div></blockquote><br>
You.  And probably OBF.  If I really have to spell out why I put Greg at L-1 please ask.

I'll take snifit tomorrow if there's no movement on the charter wagon.<br>
@Shadoweh: Look at Charter ISO. He has a lot questions asked and non followed through too.<br>
@Charter. Town, mostly cause I can't see him being your scumbuddy.

@snifit wagon - snifit wagon needs to fall apart at the wheels ASAP.  Whether or not you personally think that his claim is truthful or scummy, it doesn't matter and is irrelevant at this point.  His truthfulness will become more than apparent after the next in-game day or two.<br>
<br>
@DV - I really can't get on you for taking the approach that you did, you can't go after snifit and you can't very well vote for yourself so you had to go outside the lines.  I'm still willing to hammer, you did the best you could with the crappy situation that OBF put you in.

@Shadoweh...you left out the option where you and Greg are both scum and his impending VT claim was a QT discussion.  He seems like the thorough type that would discuss a claim with buddies.  Though you coukd be a scum rolecop I suppose.  That would make it likely town had more PRs which would be nice.  Either way...you before Greg works better.  <br>
<br>
Who do you think is scum besides myko?  Image still?  Me?  Nacho/Caron?
